Package projecttwo

Class Date

  • java.lang.Object
    • projecttwo.Date
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Date>
    public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Date>
    This class defines a date by year, month, and day from an input String, it also auto-generates a date object with calendar date if no parameter is sent, and checks if dates are valid calendar dates based on the Calendar library
    Author:
    Aryan Jairath, Anis Chihoub
